<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 200px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .details {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvhrnkeyg/image/upload/v1740860815/banner_bjfwgd.jpg" alt="SUGRiA Logo" class="logo">
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Profile Update Confirmation</h2>
        <p>Dear {{firstName}},</p>
        
        <p>Your SUGRiA member profile has been successfully updated. Here's a summary of your updated information:</p>
        
        <div class="details">
            <p><strong>Work Email:</strong> {{workEmail}}</p>
            <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> {{phoneNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Residential Address:</strong> {{residentialAddress}}</p>
        </div>

        <p>If you notice any discrepancies or need to make further changes, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2024 Sustainable Green Revolution in Africa (SUGRiA). All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>For any inquiries, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@sugria.com">support@sugria.com</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 